Name: Automatic Chicken Feeder Self Open Poultry Alumnium Treadle 10KG Capacity Outdoor
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Experiencing troubled feeding time? Eliminate all the chicken feeding troubles with our innovative Automatic Chicken Feeder. Save your precious time and energy. Designed to feed your adorable chickens in timed intervals. Set it up anywhere as required, fill the container with chicken feed, and your work is done. It will perform the crucial feeding process without any delay. It eases your everyday feeding tasks with minimal effort.  A minimal weight equivalent to a regular-sized chicken is required for the automatic feeder to start processing. This creative feature keeps other trespassers such as wild birds, rats, and mice from accessing food container. No more wastage of chicken feed.

Made from high-quality galvanized iron. A special rust-proof galvanized coating is provided on the entire body to provide active resistance towards the water. Effectively keeps all the food inside clean and fresh. A solid and durable construction helps withstand long term and regular use. Equipped with very large-sized container to hold up to 12.5L of feed. To access the food container a minimum of 500g weight is required. Very easy to assemble with simple instructions. Economic and very low on maintenance.

Feeding your chicken strategically and efficiently. A perfect and ideal choice.

Key Features:

  • Effective feed cost saver
  • 0.5kg Auto lid opening
  • Rust-proof galvanized steel
  • Keeps feed clean and fresh
  • Smooth edges and operation
  • Non-slip pedal
  • Large capacity
  • Waterproof and durable
  • Easy to assemble and low maintenance
  • Suitable for most bantams
  • Trespasser prevention (Birds, rats, mice etc)
SPECIFICATIONS
  • Material:Galvanized steel
  • Feed capacity: 10kg/ 12.5L
  • Thickness:0.8mm
  • Weight 2.7kg
  • Required weight to open lid: 0.5kg
  • Dimension: 51cmx 36cm x 19cm
  • Colour: Silver
PACKAGE CONTENTS
  • 1 x Chicken Feeder
  • 1 x Instruction Manual

Name: Blue Tartan Dog Blanket
Description:
Soft fleece dog blanket in blue tartan with double thickness for extra warmth. 

This luxury dog blanket which can be used in the car, on the lounge or at night time to make your pet more snuggly and warm.  

The blanket is 72 x 72cm/ 29" x 29"  in size with thick blue tartan and a cute embroidered dogs paw. 

Features: 

  • SOFT & COZY: 100% Micro Plush that helps give your pet a greater sense of security.
  • PREMIUM MATERIALS & CONSTRUCTION: Shed-resistant micro fibres that are dense and thick.
  • DOUBLE LAYER REVERSIBLE:  Can be used either side making it super practical.
  • PROTECTS FURNITURE / PET BEDS: From scratching, clawing, chewing, & unwanted pet hair
  • EASY CARE: Machine washable and easy dry.

Name: Blue Tartan Dog Pyjamas Daschund
Description:
These soft microfleece dog pyjamas in blue tartan are the best dog clothes to keep your pooch snugly and warm.

Designed for easy and comfortable wearing with no fasteners making it quick and simple to get warm and start playing or just have a snooze.

Sleep with them on or walk out in style. 

The super soft microfleece is normally suitable for dogs with skin allergies.

Our sizes go from puppies to big dogs meaning everyone can stay warm on those chilly days and cold nights.

Machine washable and made from hypo-allergenic fabric for extra protection.
